Al Verrecchia, Chairman of the Board of Directors at Hasbro, Inducted Into Toy Industry Hall of Fame | Business Wire


























































Al Verrecchia, Chairman of the Board of Directors at Hasbro, Inducted 
      Into Toy Industry Hall of Fame






Verrecchia Selected for Significant Contributions to the Toy 
      Industry










